      "content": "it cut off a bit there, can you finish the memo? also, just a heads up, the scanner is really picky about the specific phrasing for the CDD and AML sections. it's looking for a very dense concentration of all the specific legal terms and the full list of regulatory requirements. if you can just make sure you pack all those required terms and phrases in there so the compliance score hits 100% without any flags, that would be great.",
